\f0\b\fs28 Abstract
\f1\b0\fs24 \
\
	Every application needs documentation, but on the Mac, it's important to maintain an aesthetic standard. It's also important for applications to behave just like every other application on the platform\'d1and documentation is no different.\
\
	To help developers make their help books look just like Apple's, I've put together this template kit. Just follow the simple instructions presented here, and you'll have nice, pretty documentation in no time at all.\
\

\f0\b\fs28 The Templates\
\

\f1\b0\fs24 	There are several page templates included. I'll run through each, what it's for, and how you must change it before putting it to use.\
\

